title: Red Track Rankings (The Finale) (13's Version)
description:
IT IS THE END OF AN ERA! We take one last official deep dive into the Red (Taylor's Version) album.. Which tracks do we think are the best? And what tracks are your favs?
Let us know, and let us know what you would like to hear from us while we tread and wait for another announcement. We are going to do some fun episodes while we wait!
Hit us up and let us know everything!
